OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly feeling day. There
OL,6,Fwill be some bright spells, but it'll
OL,7,Foften be cloudy with blustery, locally
OL,8,Fheavy showers and a risk of hail.
OL,9,FDriest in the south and west. A brisk
OL,10,Fnortherly wind adding to the colder
OL,11,Ffeel.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers easing but persisting
OL,14,Fovernight with the brisk northerly
OL,15,Fwind continuing. Rather chilly, but
OL,16,Fthe wind and cloud preventing a frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
