OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FWinds will gradually ease
OL,6,Fthrough the day, but scattered,
OL,7,Fblustery showers continue with some
OL,8,Fwith hail and thunder possible.
OL,9,FTemperatures remaining below average
OL,10,Ffor mid-May.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDrier
OL,13,Fand brighter on Friday and Saturday
OL,14,Fwith perhaps the odd shower, winds
OL,15,Fmostly light too. Rain arriving from
OL,16,Fthe west on Sunday. Temperatures
OL,17,Fslowly increasing, but still below
OL,18,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
